{"tid":251123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個On9 班會事件","createTime":"2017-05-20T15:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T01:32:20.000Z","uid":117993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69b8471e7afbf47549d2e7e7d5de66860cdf300c","tid":251123,"uid":117993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"話說我班會有一次開Party ，主席問大家要食咩，大家粒聲唔出，到凖備落訂，班撚人先出聲，話要食218，然後其中一條臭化西屌主席極權，條友本來係爭主席爭輸咗，佢又懶係做好多野，懶係委屈，仲要馬撚咁串，串鳩主席唔聽民意，明明一早問哂又無人出聲，條臭化西講兩句又出嚟話主席獨裁，結果嗰日主席要再去訂嘢食，仲要整唔同嘅嘢食，五點入東涌幫人拎嘢，一早講咪冇事囉！"},{"pid":"cc98b95d25299e9e000121b08ae7fcdc6164c3c8","tid":251123,"uid":43127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"整件班衫投幾次票，三年唔同款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n團結極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d83c14c071a17e78d0582fe44c53c11b77b227e","tid":251123,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"開波嗰陣全班懶撚齊心話要參加singing contest<br />\n到排舞排位完全無人 仲一齊屌番個搞手轉頭"},{"pid":"766c1c64282cb2e50b620cc79bd951a64b4d8d65","tid":251123,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"強制收班會費就最戇鳩"},{"pid":"9a18ca2b7afeea01ceb7fb9901b4e96781ef5237","tid":251123,"uid":117993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強制收班會費就最戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"798bb0eaf6fc1fca1ffa142598d402e7e1b5ad7e","tid":251123,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"班際Sing Con決定唱主能夠10分鐘版<br />\n結果俾校長走入班房鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0389246536878b415629ad0f4de98c383cd290ca","tid":251123,"uid":84494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班際Sing Con決定唱主能夠10分鐘版<br />\n結果俾校長走入班房鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.